Hi {{buyer_name}},

Receipt for your records:

- Order: {{order_id}}
- Date: {{date}}
- Item: {{item_title}}
- Total paid: {{amount}}
- Seller: Syndrax marketplace seller

Thanks for your purchase,
{{seller_signoff}}

Hi {{buyer_name}},

Thanks for your order ({{order_id}}) for **{{item_title}}**.

I’m sorry — this item is no longer available to ship. I’ve started a full refund / cancellation so you aren’t left waiting.

{{similar_note}}

Sorry again for the inconvenience,
{{seller_signoff}}

Hi {{buyer_name}},

Your order **{{order_id}}** is on the way.

- Carrier: {{carrier}}
- Tracking: {{tracking}}
- ETA: {{eta}}

You can follow the package with the tracking number above. Message me if anything looks off after delivery day.

Thanks,
{{seller_signoff}}
